reviewtext: Bought these headphones by mistake.. was originally going to buy something with volume control but for some reasons ordered these Panasonics. Anyways i have put them in good use.. i used my shure e2c earbuds on my laptop but now i'm using these $6 comfy headphones because my ears don't hurt anymore. i didn't release it before.. i guess my ears got used to earbuds but after using these headphones i feel much comfier.
